description:
This listing is for one pillow.  The pattern you receive will be unique and will vary from those pictured.

Each pillow is carefully handmade, filled with flaxseed from local Amish farmers and finished with an adorable vintage button!

Store them in your freezer or warm them in the microwave for the most indulgent experience! The pillow cover is removable and washable. These pillows are unscented for those who have sensitive skin. 

Our custom body & linen splash is the perfect item to accompany our eye pillows if you are desiring a fragrance. Our favorites: lavendar & fresh herbs, eucalyptus or nag champa.

name: Coconut and Brown Sugar Scrub 8oz in Ball Jar
description:
Coconut and Brown Sugar Scrub in a new Recyclable 8oz Ball Glass Jar with wooden spoon!

If you are looking for a soothing skin therapy option, this sugar scrub is a must! I use it daily on my hands...it not only moisturizes dry skin, but provides a little mini massage! 

I use pure unrefined Nutiva coconut oil. If you have ever used Nutiva, you will know this is top quality!

Current studies are showing Coconut Oil to be one of the most healthy oils in the world and current studies have proven sugar to be a natural antioxidant. This AMAZING scrub combines both for an invigorating skincare experience!



Directions:
Use 2-3 times a week for face, hands and body. Scrub gently for 3 minutes and rinse clean with warm water. Pat dry with a towel. 

If you want to keep your skin soft and moisturized, this product is perfect!

Go to www.coconutresearchcenter.org for great information about coconut oil!

Ingredients: Pure Unrefined Organic Nutiva Coconut Oil (Lauric Acid), Organic Brown Sugar, Molasses
